OL,3,C'I fear for my life': Man still
OL,4,Cwaiting on triple hernia surgery after
OL,5,Csix years
OL,7,FWinston Baldwin has been living with a
OL,8,Ftriple hernia since 2019, which has
OL,9,Fnow grown so large he can now barely
OL,10,Fwalk and needs a wheelchair to get
OL,11,Faround.
OL,13,FHe has faced constant delays, made
OL,14,Fworse by the pandemic, and says his
OL,15,Fsituation is becoming increasingly
OL,16,Fdifficult, leaving him without hope.
OL,18,FAfter repeated cancellations he now
OL,19,Flives in a care home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
