OL,3,C'I fear for my life': Man still
OL,4,Cwaiting on triple hernia surgery after
OL,5,Csix years
OL,7,FHe is feeling increasingly desperate:
OL,8,F"The wait has been insufferable and
OL,9,FI've been hoping from May 2019 it will
OL,10,Fget done and it didn't and its grown
OL,11,Fbigger."
OL,13,FHe adds: "I've lived in hope, hope
OL,14,Fthat one day I can go back to my life.
OL,16,F"I feel let down from the word go
OL,17,Fbecause I was promised an operation.
OL,19,F"The NHS should have taken me
OL,20,Fseriously and they haven't."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
