OL,3,C'I fear for my life': Man still
OL,4,Cwaiting on triple hernia surgery after
OL,5,Csix years
OL,7,FHe finds it a struggle to breathe or
OL,8,Fget out of his wheelchair, and he says
OL,9,Fthis must be the year he gets his
OL,10,Foperation
OL,12,F"I don't feel they are listening...I
OL,13,Fneed help, I need attention, thats
OL,14,Fwhat I've needed from 2019.
OL,16,F"Its a downward spiral that I'm living
OL,17,Fon, and I'm living on borrowed
OL,18,Ftime...I fear for my life, I fear for
OL,19,Fmy my future."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
