OL,3,C'I fear for my life': Man still
OL,4,Cwaiting on triple hernia surgery after
OL,5,Csix years
OL,7,FWinston feels his quality of life has
OL,8,Fbeen destroyed, and he just wants it
OL,9,Fback.
OL,11,FHis story has been featured on ITV
OL,12,FGranada Reports five times, ever since
OL,13,Fhis treatment was delayed in 2019
OL,14,Fduring Covid.
OL,16,FDuring the General Election
OL,17,Fcampaigning now Prime Minister Sir
OL,18,FKeir Starmer said Winston's then five
OL,19,Fyear wait for a hernia operation was a
OL,20,F"shocking indictment" of NHS waiting
OL,21,Flists and the longest he has heard of.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
