OL,3,C'I fear for my life': Man still
OL,4,Cwaiting on triple hernia surgery after
OL,5,Csix years
OL,7,FHe personally vowed to help sort out
OL,8,Fwaiting times to help his plight.
OL,10,FSpeaking at the time, he said it was
OL,11,F"appalling".
OL,13,F"I would say to Winston, it's
OL,14,Fappalling you've been waiting for five
OL,15,Fyears for a hernia operation," he said
OL,16,Fin June 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
