OL,3,C'I fear for my life': Man still
OL,4,Cwaiting on triple hernia surgery after
OL,5,Csix years
OL,7,F"That's one of the longest waits I've
OL,8,Fheard of even in this campaign, it's a
OL,9,Fshocking indictment of just how bad
OL,10,Fthis government has allowed the
OL,11,Fwaiting lists to get.
OL,13,F"Now we will on day one roll up our
OL,14,Fsleeves and start to repair that by
OL,15,Fputting in place extra NHS staff to
OL,16,Fget those appointments done soo that
OL,17,FWinston can get the operation he
OL,18,Fdesperately needs."
